---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Container from '../../components/Container.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="World of Dinosaurs — Khonsu Development"
  description="Explore dinosaurs and prehistoric animals with articles, illustrations, quizzes, discovery sites, and more."
  canonicalPath="/dinosaurs"
>
  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16">
    <Container>
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <article class="prose prose-invert max-w-none prose-headings:tracking-tight prose-p:text-zinc-200 prose-li:text-zinc-200">
          <h1>Welcome to World of Dinosaurs</h1>
          <p>A tribute to all the animals that roamed our planet before us.</p>
          <p>Learn all about dinosaurs and prehistoric animals with World of Dinosaurs.</p>

          <p>
            Introducing World of Dinosaurs — packed with tons of information, fun quizzes, and features to help you explore
            the fascinating world of dinosaurs and prehistoric animals.
          </p>

          <h2>Features</h2>
          <p>
            With World of Dinosaurs, access an extensive library of articles and illustrations — from behavior and habitat
            to unique characteristics — including popular dinosaurs and lesser-known species.
          </p>

          <h3>Broad list of animals</h3>
          <p>
            Discover <strong>1900+ prehistoric animals</strong>: dinosaurs, pterosaurs, aquatic titans, but also extinct
            animals of the Cenozoic — closer to us and just as fascinating.
          </p>

          <h3>Extensive information</h3>
          <p>
            Detailed descriptions, lifelike images, size comparisons, habitat info, and fun trivia to bring prehistoric
            giants to life.
          </p>

          <h3>Go back in time</h3>
          <p>Explore billions of years in the life of planet Earth with the interactive Geological Time Scale.</p>

          <h3>Articles</h3>
          <p>Stories across prehistoric lives, extinction, fossils, and new research.</p>

          <p>
            World of Dinosaurs also offers interactive quizzes — great for experts and beginners — with hours of learning
            and entertainment.
          </p>

          <h3>Tailored quiz</h3>
          <p>Customize quizzes: match names, identify images, or dive into fascinating dino facts.</p>

          <h3>Learn about your favourite animals</h3>
          <p>Different quizzes for different categories of prehistoric animals.</p>

          <h3>Discovery sites</h3>
          <p>Explore fossil digging sites from around the world, and find which animals were found close to you.</p>

          <h3>Dark mode</h3>
          <p>
            Sleek elegance and eye comfort — reduce eye strain, save battery, and enjoy a modern interface tailored for
            night-time or all-day use.
          </p>

          <blockquote>
            <p>“Dinosaurs may be extinct from the face of the planet, but they are alive and well in our imaginations.”</p>
            <p>— Steve Miller</p>
          </blockquote>

          <p>
            If you found a bug or a content error, please report it to{' '}
            <a href="mailto:khonsu.development@gmail.com">khonsu.development@gmail.com</a>.
          </p>
        </article>

        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center">
          <a
            class="btn btn-primary"
            href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=eu.khonsu.dinosaurs"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            target="_blank"
          >
            Get it on Google Play
          </a>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/apps/world-of-dinosaurs">
            View on this site
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-10 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <a class="underline decoration-white/20 underline-offset-4 hover:text-white" href="/dinosaurs/terms-and-conditions-for-world-of-dinosaurs">
            Terms &amp; Conditions for World of Dinosaurs
          </a>
          {' · '}
          <a class="underline decoration-white/20 underline-offset-4 hover:text-white" href="/dinosaurs/privacy-policy-for-world-of-dinosaurs">
            Privacy Policy for World of Dinosaurs
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
